head: Autostrada del Sole
trans(no paren):
The A1 motorway from Milan to Naples
 2002 Zeffiro Ciuffoletti - Paesaggi toscani 
 After the construction if the Italian railway system, the great infrastructural innovations arrived with the expressways and in particular with the Autostrada del Sole, which crossed Tuscany from the Apennines to the Valdichiana, runing through lovely landscapes.
